      "writtenOn": "2020-01-05T03:07:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I am not sold on the term \"wedge\"; these are synonymous with the patches that the are processed by the tessellation shader, right? If so, could we just call them GrAnchoredCurvePatchGen?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 18,
