      "lineNbr": 18,
      "author": {
        "id": 5633
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-01-06T16:41:31Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I actually quite liked the term \"wedge\". I like how it describes the geometry that grows outward from the center point of the path. What issue do you take with it?",
