      "writtenOn": "2020-01-06T17:23:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "FWIW I\u0027m pro-wedge. Wedge doesn\u0027t really conflict with existing adjacent jargon AFAIK and it seems useful to have a short word to refer to these things. Sometimes we get to make up our own lingo in our own domain.",
